{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2204ac2f5a","title":"中共中央关于中发［73］14号文件传达范围的通知","origin":"根据中央文件原件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ba980793e3","index":0,"year":1973,"month":4,"day":3,"articleId":"2204ac2f5a"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"5bd9678625","name":"邓小平","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"25c50e04ee","type":"title","text":"中共中央关于中发［1973］14号文件传达范围的通知","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2204ac2f5a"},{"id":"354a3c2c9a","type":"paragraph","text":"一，中发［1973］14号文件是按县团级文件发的，可以口头传达全文到党员干部和非党员干部。并进行讨论。","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2204ac2f5a"},{"id":"dfa4cc2bbe","type":"paragraph","text":"二、中央关于恢复邓小平同志党的组织生活和国务院副总理的职务的决定［不包括邓小平同志的信和《我的自述》（摘录）两个附件］，可以口头传达到党内外群众，并加解释。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2204ac2f5a"},{"id":"27b61ee9e6","type":"paragraph","text":"三，对爱国人士，由各省、市、自治区和中央各部门负责人，按照本通知第二条规定，向他们作传达、解释。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2204ac2f5a"}],"page":{"id":"8968ea1484","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2204ac2f5a","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}